Tantalum-tools is a repository containing some utility programs I've
written for various projects. Some of these tools are designed to be
efficient while others are designed to take the least amount of code.

Utilities
------------------------------------------------------------------------
kTa.py:
  NAME
    kTa - Kill Named Threads

  SIZE
    1.4 KiB

  SYNOPSIS
    python kTa.py 'term1' 'term2' ...

  DESCRIPTION
    Kills processes with a name that contains at least one search term.
